{"tid":2349670,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"真係好感激香港仲有rubberband 堅持企硬","createTime":"2021-01-01T16:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T16:42:11.000Z","uid":9394,"like":413,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"ea33a95c44df43de48c3f74c80c759bc7bd77fac","tid":2349670,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:56:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6yaa6tYELZM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6yaa6tYELZM&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gapJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=be5c98e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6yaa6tYELZM</a><br />\n老實講rubberband啲歌都唔係首首岩聽<br />\n名氣都唔算係最hit (個人認為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n但佢地都作左幾首歌叫香港人撐住<br />\n希望大家都收到<br />\n香港人 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然仲有好多歌手都企硬 一齊支持佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n與其拗邊個應唔應該拎獎 <br />\n不如一齊比支持佢地 講下佢地要點改善 一齊做好香港音樂<br />\n香港民族要靠共同文化要維繫住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b030b0c9564d9e518fcfa688865f1728e2ef3bd","tid":2349670,"uid":35910,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:58:41.000Z","msg":"呢D Po先要推<br />\n咁公開表態係有料"},{"pid":"db71d58aaaeb771a3ddc5910935eb1a57c8895c7","tid":2349670,"uid":78612,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:58:57.000Z","msg":"漫長真係一首好激昂既歌<br />\n<br />\n咩時代就會有咩既時代曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55352720026fb329578a6a2f669a32973b8f1af","tid":2349670,"uid":109032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\